  "title": "Senior DevOps Engineer",
  "description": "<p><em>Temus was established by Temasek in partnership with UST, to provide digital transformation solutions for the private and public sectors as we aspire to be a strategic partner in realising the Singapore Government’s Smart Nation vision. We are headquartered in Singapore and have more than 400 employees across a wide range of disciplines in strategy, design, architecture, technology, data & AI.</em><br /></p><p><u><strong>Roles & Responsibilities:</strong></u></p><ul><li>Building and setting up and maintenance development tools and infrastructure in CI/CD landscape</li><li>Working on ways to automate and improve development and release processes</li><li>Maintain and adopt Agile best practices and lifecycles for process workflows (e.g., Kanban, CI/CD)</li><li>Work with Developers and DevOps Engineers on code review through continuous inspection, defining test scope and feature test cases based on requirements</li><li>Ensure proper process workflow is followed in accordance with internal controls, compliance, and audit requirements</li><li>Interact with clients and development teams on product backlog prioritization for software upgrades, patches and hotfix, defect fixes and enhancements</li><li>Take ownership of all issues and outages. Track and monitor issues progress until their completion and provide timely issue escalation to relevant audiences</li></ul><p><br /><u><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></u></p><ul><li>Minimum 5 years of relevant experience in DevOps/SRE, systems engineering, build/ release/ deployment automation, etc</li><li>Experience with SysOps, knowledge of scripting languages such as Java, JavaScript, Perl, Ruby, Python, PHP, Groovy, Bash</li><li>Experience designing and working with modern CI/CD with gitlab, github or jenkins or equivalent</li><li>Experience in integrating DevSecOps tool like Nexus, Fortify into Build pipelines will be an added advantage</li><li>Experience with latest tools and technologies like Docker, Kubernetes, Ansible</li><li>Experience in deploying Infrastructure as Code with Terraform or scripts to Nutanix, SCOM and equivalent</li><li>Self-motivated, hands-on, dynamic, and detail-oriented individual with a strong technical background</li></ul><p></p><p><em>By applying for this role, you have read and acknowledge the data privacy statement via this link - </em><a href=\"https://www.temus.com/job-applicant-data-protection/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">https://www.temus.com/job-applicant-data-protection/</a></p>",
